    user_response: "Apply the \"Professional Polish\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Professional Polish\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col h-screen w-full bg-slate-100 font-sans overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <header class=\\\"h-16 bg-[#034226] text-white flex items-center justify-between px-8 border-b-4 border-[#e1b12c] shadow-md shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center p-1\\\">\\n        <svg viewBox=\\\"0 0 100 100\\\" class=\\\"w-full h-full text-[#034226]\\\"><circle cx=\\\"50\\\" cy=\\\"50\\\" r=\\\"45\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\" /><path d=\\\"M50 5 L50 95 M5 50 L95 50\\\" stroke=\\\"white\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\"/><circle cx=\\\"50\\\" cy=\\\"50\\\" r=\\\"15\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"white\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\"/></svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase\\\">Polla Mundialista <span class=\\\"text-[#e1b12c]\\\">FOE</span></h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs opacity-80 leading-none\\\">Puntaje Total</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg font-bold text-[#e1b12c]\\\">145 pts</p>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#02331d] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/20\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Camilo Rodriguez</span>\\n        <img src=\\\"https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Camilo+Rodriguez&background=e1b12c&color=034226\\\" class=\\\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full border border-white\\\" alt=\\\"Profile\\\">\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-6 p-6 overflow-hidden bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-slate-200 via-slate-100 to-slate-100\\\">\\n    <section class=\\\"flex-[1.8] flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Pron\303\263sticos Pendientes</h2>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"px-3 py-1 bg-white border border-slate-300 rounded text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600\\\">Fase de Grupos</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-3 py-1 bg-[#034226] text-white rounded text-xs font-semibold\\\">8vos de Final</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-2 flex flex-col gap-3\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-50 px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200 flex justify-between\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400\\\">JUE 11-06 \342\200\242 15:00 \342\200\242 GRUPO A</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#e1b12c]\\\">PENDIENTE</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 grid grid-cols-3 items-center\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-12 h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-slate-400\\\">MEX</div>\\n              <span class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-700\\\">M\303\251xico</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2\\\">\\n              <input type=\\\"number\\\" placeholder=\\\"0\\\" class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-center text-xl font-bold focus:border-[#034226] outline-none\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-slate-300 font-bold\\\">-</span>\\n              <input type=\\\"number\\\" placeholder=\\\"0\\\" class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-center text-xl font-bold focus:border-[#034226] outline-none\\\">\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-700\\\">USA</span>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-12 h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-slate-400\\\">USA</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"px-4 pb-4\\\">\\n            <button class=\\\"w-full bg-[#034226] hover:bg-[#02331d] text-white py-2 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm transition-colors\\\">GUARDAR APUESTA</button>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden opacity-80 grayscale-[0.5]\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-100 px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200 flex justify-between\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Resultados Anteriores</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-600 tracking-wider text-right\\\">+5 PUNTOS GANADOS</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 grid grid-cols-3 items-center\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-12 h-8 bg-[#034226] rounded border border-[#034226] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white\\\">ARG</div>\\n              <span class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-700\\\">Argentina</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-center gap-3\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800\\\">2</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-slate-400\\\">VS</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800\\\">1</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-slate-400 font-bold mt-1 uppercase\\\">Marcador Exacto</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-700 uppercase\\\">Francia</span>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-12 h-8 bg-[#034226] rounded border border-[#034226] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white\\\">FRA</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-50 px-4 py-2 border-b border-slate-200 flex justify-between\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400\\\">VIE 12-06 \342\200\242 20:00 \342\200\242 GRUPO B</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#e1b12c]\\\">ABIERTO</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 grid grid-cols-3 items-center\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-12 h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-slate-400\\\">BRA</div>\\n              <span class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-700\\\">Brasil</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2\\\">\\n              <input type=\\\"number\\\" value=\\\"3\\\" class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-center text-xl font-bold\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-slate-300 font-bold\\\">-</span>\\n              <input type=\\\"number\\\" value=\\\"0\\\" class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-center text-xl font-bold\\\">\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-end gap-4\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-700\\\">Qatar</span>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-12 h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-slate-400\\\">QAT</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"px-4 pb-4\\\">\\n            <button class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-400 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm cursor-not-allowed\\\">ACTUALIZAR APUESTA</button>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <aside class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col gap-6 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col h-full gap-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\